title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine: Watch Amy Prep for Her Super-Unsexy Photo Shoot
text: Brooklyn Nine-Nine: Watch Amy Prep for Her Super-Unsexy Photo Shoot Saturday, 10 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) Cops with an image problem? No problem! On Sunday's episode of Brooklyn Nine-Nine, Captain Holt (Andre Braugher) thinks he has the perfect solution to the police's unsavory reputation: create a positive image campaign featuring NYPD's finest. Naturally, that brown-noser Amy Santiago (Melissa Fumero) will be the first detective featured. Brooklyn Nine-Nine is feeling the love in Season 3 Amy will need a little coaching though (uptight much?), and Holt is here to help. What could possibly go wrong? Take a look: Brooklyn Nine-Nine airs Sundays at 8:30/7:30c on Fox. Other Links From TVGuide.com Brooklyn Nine-NineMelissa Fumero
